                <head>Warlike Rumors</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Reports rumors surrounding the suspicious movement of Federal troops. The
                    Spectator suspects these troops are bound for Texas to reinforce the frontier
                    against Indians and Mexicans.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
