                <head>Immediate Secession</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>A resolution offered in the Convention on Thursday called for the
                    Convention to adopt an Ordinance of Secession and to submit it to the people in
                    the May elections. The resolution was defeated 89 to 45.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
